  characterName: Clay
  doubts:
  - doubtId: 0
    doubtText: I remember when these hills were wild. Untouched. Now I barely recognize
      the roots beneath my feet. Have I lingered too long in a world that no longer
      needs me?
    options:
    - optionId: 0
      option: You could always leave.
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 1
      option: You helped shape this world.
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 2
      option: You've done enough.
      itemsRequired: []
    correctOptionId: 1
    doubtSuccessResponse: "I shaped it\u2026 and I was shaped by it. That is true.
      Perhaps my story still grows, even if it\u2019s no longer the same soil."
    doubtFailureResponse: ...
  - doubtId: 1
    doubtText: "The garden calls to me, but not in words I understand. Magic\u2026
      Alchemy\u2026 What place do I have in tending something I cannot know?"
    options:
    - optionId: 0
      option: Trust the ones who can understand it
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 1
      option: Alchemy is just weeds with glitter.
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 2
      option: Step back. Let it be.
      itemsRequired: []
    correctOptionId: 0
    doubtSuccessResponse: "To trust another\u2019s hands, even when I cannot feel
      what they feel. That takes more than patience. That takes faith. But perhaps
      I am capable."
    doubtFailureResponse: ...
  - doubtId: 2
    doubtText: "I have seen countless cycles\u2014growth, decay, rebirth. Yet I never
      change. What if I am not part of life\u2019s circle, but just its stone border?"
    options:
    - optionId: 0
      option: Even stone can bloom moss.
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 1
      option: In time, you will change.
      itemsRequired: []
    - optionId: 2
      option: You were never part of the circle.
      itemsRequired: []
    correctOptionId: 0
    doubtSuccessResponse: "Moss\u2026 Yes. Quiet life upon unmoving rock. I had forgotten.
      Perhaps I do change\u2014just more slowly than most."
    doubtFailureResponse: ...
